fields.comment: Is final claim for fiscal year

fields.name: egcs_fc_periodend
fields.comment: The last month of the payment period

fields.name: egcs_fc_periodstart
fields.comment: The first month of the payment period

fields.name: egcs_fc_holdback
fields.comment: The percentage of either the total agreement value or the final year fiscal year value that will be withheld until the final payment

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalclaimstolastclaimmonth
fields.comment: The total value of all processed claims for the agreement

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalforecasttolastclaimmonth
fields.comment: The total forecast amount for all months up to and including the last month for which a processed claim exists

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalshortfall
fields.comment: = [Total Claims to Last Claim Month]  [Total Forecast to Last Claim Month] (if the amount is negative, it is slippage, meaning it will be subtracted from the payment total; if the amount is positive, it is a shortfall, meaning the recipient did not forecast enough and it will be added to the payment total)

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalforecasttoperiodend
fields.comment: The total forecast amount for all months up to and including the last month of the payment period

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalpaymentstodate
fields.comment: The total value of all processed payments for the agreement

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalnextadvancepayment
fields.comment: = [Total Forecast to Period End]  [Total Payments to Date] (the value of the advance payment based on the forecast before accounting for the shortfall)

fields.name: egcs_fc_previousclaimstotal
fields.comment: If there are claims for the agreement that were processed outside of the system, the amount will be reflected here and added to the total claimed amount in the calculation

fields.name: egcs_fc_previouspamentstotal
fields.comment: If there are payments for the agreement that were processed outside of the system, the amount will be reflected here and added to the total paid amount in the calculation

fields.name: egcs_fc_holdbackamount
fields.comment: = [Total Agreement Value] OR [Final Year Fiscal Value] * [Holdback %]

fields.name: egcs_fc_availablefordisbursement
fields.comment: = [Total Claimed] + [Total Forecast for Unclaimed Months in Current FY] + [Total FY Value of Future Fiscal Years]  [Total Payments]  [Holdback Amount] (i.e. the amount of money that can be paid before the Holdback threshold is reached)

fields.name: egcs_fc_payeavailablefordisbursement
fields.comment: For PAYE payments, this is the total amount of unpaid money remaining in the PAYE commitment

fields.name: egcs_fc_paye2availablefordisbursement
fields.comment: For PAYE2 payments, this is the total amount of unpaid money remaining on the PAYE2 commitment line

fields.name: egcs_fc_previousyearpayeavaialblefordisbursement
fields.comment: For previous-year PAYE payments (i.e. PAYEs for a fiscal year that is two years ago or earlier), this is the total amount of unpaid money remaining in the PYP commitment

fields.name: egcs_fc_commitmentavailablefordisbursement
fields.comment: For standard payments, this is the total amount of unpaid money remaining on the commitment line(s) for the current fiscal year

fields.name: egcs_fc_totalsystemcalculatedamount
fields.comment:
For reimbursements, = [Total Claims to Last Claim Month] minus [Total Payments to Date]
 For advances, = [Total Shortfall] + [Total Next Advance Payment]

fields.name: egcs_fc_holdbackrelease
fields.comment: The amount of the holdback that is being released as part of the payment, either because it is the final payment or the Release Holdback manual override is engaged

fields.name: egcs_fc_paymentamount
fields.comment:
The total payment amount. It is equal to the lower of:
  
 Available for Disbursement (except for the final payment or payments where the Release Holdback manual override is engaged) 
 PAYE Available for Disbursement (PAYE payments only)
 PAYE2 Available for Disbursement (PAYE2 payments only)
 PYP Available for Disbursement (PYP payments only)
 Commit. Available for Disbursement (standard payments only)
 Total System Calculated Amount
